content: this headband is knit in the round with two contrasting colors it is a quick knit and great for using up small amounts of special yarn i hope you enjoy this free pattern thank you so much for all your support this year i so deeply appreciate it **approximate yardage** mc 65 yards 59 meters cc 50 yards 46 meters **note** this free pattern has not been tech edited or tested please contact me if you notice any errors or have any questions
